  preserve-subst' {n} {T} {S} {Δ} {(Var m)} {s} {v} (TVar{m} x) j'
    with extract{n}{Δ}{S ∷ []}{T}{m} x
  ...  | in-Δ x₁
       with m ≟ᴺ length Δ
  ...     | yes p = contradiction p (<⇒≢ (var-env-< x₁))
  ...     | no ¬p
          with m <ᴺ? length Δ
  ...        | yes p' = TVar x₁
  ...        | no ¬p' = contradiction (var-env-< x₁) ¬p'
  preserve-subst' {n} {T} {S} {Δ} {(Var m)} {s} {v} (TVar{m} x) j'
       | in-Γ x₁ x₂
       with m ≟ᴺ length Δ
  ...     | yes p
          with ext{n}{[]}{Δ} j'
  ...        | w
               rewrite p
                   | (env-type-equiv x)
                   | (closed-no-shift {n} {+ length Δ} {0} {s} j')
                   | (A++[]≡A{lzero}{Ty}{Δ})
